 Use Jackson Annotations
 Add these annotations from com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation:
 
 
// In Parent
@OneToMany(mappedBy = "parent", cascade = CascadeType.ALL)
@JsonManagedReference
private List<Child> children;

// In Child
@ManyToOne
@JsonBackReference
private Parent parent;


@JsonManagedReference: serialize this side (children)
@JsonBackReference: skip this side (parent) during serialization
----------------------------------------------------------------------------